    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用电力十足的新成员保持你的殖民地与时俱进！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《仿生增幅包》</strong>通过新的仿生复制人、增强技能的仿生增幅块、便携式电力存储以及远程作业建筑彻底革新了劳动力形式——这正是你创造宇宙规模的殖民地所需要的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/365812030a42679fb7571d80b113045a.poster.avif?t=1734027577\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/365812030a42679fb7571d80b113045a.webm?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/365812030a42679fb7571d80b113045a.mp4?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在低可呼吸度环境中安全地采集资源！仿生复制人内部存有氧气，能工作数个周期都不用换气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/29a4e176b8714d0055ff87fd94840b2c.poster.avif?t=1734027577\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/29a4e176b8714d0055ff87fd94840b2c.webm?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/29a4e176b8714d0055ff87fd94840b2c.mp4?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构建仿生体！混合搭配增幅块以自定义仿生复制人的技能组，并根据殖民地不断变化的需求将其重新组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要确保这些新复制人干燥，同时也不要在仿生保养站上吝啬。传统的厕所并不是为他们设计的……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/f996a9e779f2cc2bff58a4490fda3d88.poster.avif?t=1734027577\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/f996a9e779f2cc2bff58a4490fda3d88.webm?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/f996a9e779f2cc2bff58a4490fda3d88.mp4?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该脱离电网了！新的便携式移动电源不仅能让仿生复制人保持在线，在与新的供电建筑之一连接时，还能为你的基地孤立区域供电。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/a1f1b74a937f2de41f4b32de93c207ed.poster.avif?t=1734027577\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/a1f1b74a937f2de41f4b32de93c207ed.webm?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/a1f1b74a937f2de41f4b32de93c207ed.mp4?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >取消通勤！现在火箭可以配备新舱块从而进行无驾驶员飞行，新的远程作业建筑能让你的复制人在小行星上的任意位置操作机械。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在通勤上浪费的时间变少，那么就有更多时间用于真正重要的事情：工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/11cf8467890193510d65de4b6b3cd241.poster.avif?t=1734027577\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/11cf8467890193510d65de4b6b3cd241.webm?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/11cf8467890193510d65de4b6b3cd241.mp4?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你的小行星个性化！新的修饰性皮肤能改变自动化组件、电路等东西的外观。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/5dc785716e46ff5224b8caf6cd970082.poster.avif?t=1734027577\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/5dc785716e46ff5224b8caf6cd970082.webm?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302470/extras/5dc785716e46ff5224b8caf6cd970082.mp4?t=1734027577\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的仿生成员、远程作业选择、便携式电力方案——用<strong>《仿生增幅包》</strong>为你的星际探索提供不竭动力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
